{"tid":1467272,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"知唔知5年前輸咩呀？捉鬼、割蓆、篤灰、分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:59:47.000Z","uid":179379,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"46c60dae16a81d98558847d886424ab8fb1aee15","tid":1467272,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"無錯呀，各位一日之內就犯晒全部啦<br />\n今日有做過以上行為嘅，全部同我冷靜完再反省吓<br />\n<br />\n811拉嘅好多被私刑打到斷骨<br />\n啱啱先有幾個手足喺機場俾狗拉咗<br />\n黑警仲掹咗槍真槍想射殺我哋嘅戰友<br />\n然後成個連登喺度互屌？<br />\n你對唔撚對得住佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>捉鬼</strong></ins></span><br />\n講咗好多次，一直以嚟都有鬼<br />\n只係811對家做到出面啫<br />\n但唔係激動少少就係鬼，唔啱你心水就係鬼<br />\n要捉鬼，你同我落場捉，好似捉嗰幾隻公安咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>割蓆</strong></ins></span><br />\n核彈都唔割就講到大大聲<br />\n但今日阻旅客失民意又割、打公安又割<br />\n你要明白落到場嘅戰友可能情緒比較激動<br />\n特別係今日人數同噚日有咁多反差<br />\n佢哋心急好正常，事後檢討可以，唔好屌唔好割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>篤灰</strong></ins></span><br />\n未確認係鬼，影人大頭放上嚟，呢個行徑已經係篤灰<br />\n噚日已經有幾單搞錯咗，但佢哋嘅大頭已經傳通街<br />\n所以，你未fc嘅嘢，唔好forward出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>分化</strong></ins></span><br />\n留守撚 vs 散水撚<br />\n勇武 vs 和理非<br />\n豬隊友、唔用腦、今日輸晒、運動玩完<br />\n呢啲分化嘢除咗發洩，對件事有冇幫助？<br />\n如果冇，下次開post之前同我諗清楚先開post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大家要回想返呢兩個月嚟係點合作<br />\n文宣、和理非人海、物資鏈、前線、哨兵、fa<br />\n全部都係缺一不可<br />\n軍師可以繼續提供意見，但唔好屌<br />\n前線兄弟亦都需要控制一吓情緒，盡量做最好嘅決定</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不盲目捉鬼</span>"},{"pid":"6911d614e62707f3b9b15d149306c25eced8159e","tid":1467272,"uid":95487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707cd292060e0a5c2d8e7229e3db846a6f3c2316","tid":1467272,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"我係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf69ccb86b7af3e87d9b9f6383f88021f18539e","tid":1467272,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"1a4da7d9a1e30a40fee9529b479e5de271cc97ec","tid":1467272,"uid":295761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"［請廣傳］818民陣遊行係極為重要既關鍵一戰<br />\n<br />\n當大家焦點去曬機場既時間，大家唔好唔記得818民陣既和理非遊行！呢個遊行係黎緊一場極為重要既民意授權戰！<br />\n<br />\n意義就好似外國政府要推行一項政策遇到障礙時，都會主動提前大選，取得民意授權，先至能夠俾佢繼續推行落去，例如日本首相安倍晉三前年受醜聞困擾，佢提前大選，結果大勝，上個月參議院改選又保住控制權，黎緊就會上國會推修憲令自衛隊變軍隊！ <br />\n但好似英國前首相may姐咁，佢同樣前年提前大選想攞民意推佢個脫歐方案，保住個位但議席輸到九彩，卒之挨唔住要落台，所以818遊行既人數多少，將會直接主宰呢場運動仲可唔可以走落去，所以818輸人，我地就可以收皮。<br />\n<br />\n政府亦都會睇實星期日多唔多人遊行，係風向標，少人既話就會立即全面恢復運作，甚至開turbo照過明日大愚國歌法毫無顧慮。<br />\n<br />\n所有跪求大家瘋狂廣傳，係呢幾日谷盡星期日遊行！"},{"pid":"72017aeaf79a0dcf5d739f16798d49b31bd81afc","tid":1467272,"uid":59537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:23.000Z","msg":"【有種責任叫幫口】<br />\n<br />\n開始有阻塞機場出境入閘口。<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動升級，唔好話對家，連同路人都會有一部分『頂唔順』－－心理上跟唔到。<br />\n<br />\n『咁做會失去民意支持架&hellip;』，係大家最常會跌入嘅心理盲點。<br />\n<br />\n首先，極權做嘅野，唔通民意好支持？佢地有冇倒台？<br />\n<br />\n然後，每一個人，你、我，咪就係民意囉？<br />\n<br />\n不要說『咁做會失去民意支持架&hellip;』，試著說『我就係民意！我支持推倒極權！支持爭取法治人道民主！』<br />\n<br />\n民意好重要係事實！就係因為呢個係事實，而呢場運動由開初就係兄弟爬山各自努力，不阻止不篤灰不割蓆，咁唯一一個做法就係，只要係對準極權，佢出得手，我地就幫手出口！<br />\n<br />\n到我地有其他辦法去行動時，佢地又掉返 轉頭黎幫手幫口。<br />\n<br />\n總之槍頭對外，唔好內部動搖。<br />\n<br />\n唔係邊有資格做最低成本最安全但又極重要嘅文宣部！<br />\n<br />\n大家自己諗下，呢場運動到底係仍然要處處顧忌到而家都未堅決嘅嗰部分民意，定係我地趁咁多堅定不移嘅隊友企左出黎，就一齊營造最牢不可破嘅堅實民意？<br />\n<br />\n不宜妄自菲薄，我地就係民意！<br />\n<br />\n幫口唔係不講道理只講立場，幫口正正就係講最大嘅道理、最大嘅大是大非，每一次行動升級嘅原因，唔會係因為我地暴力、我地魯莽，而只有一個真正原因：就係『極權政府一意孤行與民為敵。』<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係唔鼓勵阻離境嘅其中一員，但佢地做左，我就會幫口，因為都係針對政權，大家就係同路人。事後做檢討係事後為左件事好再反思，呢一刻做左就同行到底。<br />\n<br />\n#核爆都唔割蓆<br />\n#因為中共港共的所作所為比核爆更令我厭惡<br />\n#呢個理由夠未先"},{"pid":"8eb0aa3a85e998eeaac603d7dd406d45b19c003b","tid":1467272,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"3857584d7781754e57d2df8f6dad8e6c7653ec86","tid":1467272,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"pish 支持"},{"pid":"d628d340cccd51157feb822a090d5b0c0a1e4866","tid":1467272,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"d661903a0a29c2d32bbef783051aa4f4e38b47cb","tid":1467272,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:12.000Z","msg":"有請阿寶出場"},{"pid":"71ec47f8351e62d208a1287c3d47247897fd543d","tid":1467272,"uid":274093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acbdc728a3cbd2e4e1cbd9eef66e6c001557b0c5","tid":1467272,"uid":282197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"fb11e0d331a9c96f935174816a61fd3c77e93638","tid":1467272,"uid":64103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c60dae16a81d98558847d886424ab8fb1aee15","tid":1467272,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"無錯呀，各位一日之內就犯晒全部啦<br />\n今日有做過以上行為嘅，全部同我冷靜完再反省吓<br />\n<br />\n811拉嘅好多被私刑打到斷骨<br />\n啱啱先有幾個手足喺機場俾狗拉咗<br />\n黑警仲掹咗槍真槍想射殺我哋嘅戰友<br />\n然後成個連登喺度互屌？<br />\n你對唔撚對得住佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>捉鬼</strong></ins></span><br />\n講咗好多次，一直以嚟都有鬼<br />\n只係811對家做到出面啫<br />\n但唔係激動少少就係鬼，唔啱你心水就係鬼<br />\n要捉鬼，你同我落場捉，好似捉嗰幾隻公安咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>割蓆</strong></ins></span><br />\n核彈都唔割就講到大大聲<br />\n但今日阻旅客失民意又割、打公安又割<br />\n你要明白落到場嘅戰友可能情緒比較激動<br />\n特別係今日人數同噚日有咁多反差<br />\n佢哋心急好正常，事後檢討可以，唔好屌唔好割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>篤灰</strong></ins></span><br />\n未確認係鬼，影人大頭放上嚟，呢個行徑已經係篤灰<br />\n噚日已經有幾單搞錯咗，但佢哋嘅大頭已經傳通街<br />\n所以，你未fc嘅嘢，唔好forward出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>分化</strong></ins></span><br />\n留守撚 vs 散水撚<br />\n勇武 vs 和理非<br />\n豬隊友、唔用腦、今日輸晒、運動玩完<br />\n呢啲分化嘢除咗發洩，對件事有冇幫助？<br />\n如果冇，下次開post之前同我諗清楚先開post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大家要回想返呢兩個月嚟係點合作<br />\n文宣、和理非人海、物資鏈、前線、哨兵、fa<br />\n全部都係缺一不可<br />\n軍師可以繼續提供意見，但唔好屌<br />\n前線兄弟亦都需要控制一吓情緒，盡量做最好嘅決定</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不盲目捉鬼</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"成日叫人唔割, 做錯咗識唔識得認真去反省？"},{"pid":"478e964dc2dff3ada35b1b0199c5b886d9a3124b","tid":1467272,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"雨革嘅錯誤<br />\n一次就夠<br />\n<br />\n重覆犯錯<br />\n阿寶都頂唔順"},{"pid":"2023264a7e544443e15d4f1085fb290c9342946f","tid":1467272,"uid":188757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"前車可鑑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Za5MZ0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZa5MZ0P.jpg&h=3790966c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜撚都唔割，鬼搞事入我地數都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31380d92584ed569506558c7ecd568ce6420806b","tid":1467272,"uid":23088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0242fce902893d7f8a057b693e95bee7a40f5716","tid":1467272,"uid":295627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"唔好屌，唔好分化！<br />\n大家和理非勇武都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07846c750ef708f8dce6cdb21d2b9b631bab4e4a","tid":1467272,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"機場唔係勇武，一切以靜制動，<br />\n<br />\n唔好通宵，朝去晚返。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ab74c472fcafb9f6f6fb3d1eebf73969b6932e","tid":1467272,"uid":275278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n818post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e4b32677d55014963fd2d4b09ed393f4149ac9","tid":1467272,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山！永不割"},{"pid":"e031d6d5e0585c87f81cd4314a417cc9ac440cce","tid":1467272,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山！永不割"},{"pid":"8ad3465037d2eca1552821f6430cf9e3d3497293","tid":1467272,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ff8385b95f209ff3c90d8b3e6d44250ffcf366d","tid":1467272,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">事實就係今日都係贏<br />\n成個運動拖一日就會多一日比共產黨同港共既壓力<br />\n唔好比支那五毛打擊士氣!!!!!<br />\n港共中共同五毛既目標係消滅抗爭<br />\n佢地做法就係製造內亂打擊士氣<br />\n只要唔好自己放棄就可以玩落去<br />\n多一日贏一日 又成最大贏家了!!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e9e32818205bd4fc1944c65419366699645023c5","tid":1467272,"uid":282197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"推！正評！"},{"pid":"02b1c0d0ae53fa87b2c1dd7050e394695d95b375","tid":1467272,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"我哋唔可以輸<br />\n有6百幾個戰友被捕<br />\n有好多要逃亡海外<br />\n有人盲、有人傷殘、有無數咁多人受傷<br />\n有最少6個手足冇咗條命<br />\n仲有坐𡁵嘅天琦同一眾魚蛋嘅手足<br />\n仲有喺外國唔返得嚟嘅黃台仰、李東昇、李倩怡<br />\n<br />\n當你哋好嬲，又或者心灰意冷嘅時候<br />\n同我諗返佢哋<br />\n我哋要贏，我哋要一齊贏"}]}